DZBA004ID DIALOG LOADONCALL MOVEABLE DISCARDABLE 0,0,105,82
    STYLE 0 
     | WS_CAPTION
     | WS_SYSMENU
     | DS_MODALFRAME
    CAPTION "Details for Import/Export"
    
